Title: Looks United Waterproof Long Lasting Peel Off Mask Lip Color, Lovely Peach 15 g(Lovely Peach)
Description: Unique peel off Mask lip color to give your lips natural color and feel. Easy To Peel Off Waterproof With Long Lasting Latest Trend In Lip Color How to use? 1. Apply Touchfit along with lip line and fill in color for plumping lips. 2. Let the touchfit on your lips dry for about 5 to 10 minutes,avoiding touching lips or making lips rubbed together 3. When the product gets dry,take it off slowly from the lip ends inward. 4. After the color of Touchfit sits well on lips, finish touch with lip gloss or lip balm for moister lips.

Description: his unique 3 in 1 Face wash is meant for a deep cleansing, gentle scrubbing and perfect skin nutrition in one go . It removes excess of natural oils from the skin. Using 3 in 1 Face wash to remove dirt is a better alternative to bar soap because bar soap has a high pH (between 9 to 10), and the skin's surface pH is on average 4.7. Soap can change the balance present in the skin to favour the overgrowth of some types of bacteria, increasing acne. 3 in 1 Face wash removes the oldest dead skin cells on the skin's outermost surface by scrubbing and helps to maintain healthy skin and to reveal the newer skin beneath.
